       Orchestra smiled, he liked being complimented.

       "Yes, we must recieve orders!  Let's go, we have no time to waste!"
He said.

         Orchestra lifted Blackmightmare quickly onto his back without
saying anything and boosted off towards Zone 5.  With this femme-bot on his
back, he had a strange feeling in him.
